text:
Yesterday, the richest man in the world, @elonmusk, reminded us that he is going to dismantle the CFPB—the only federal agency dedicated solely to looking out for our nation’s consumers in the financial marketplace. 

This means that the CFPB's work to support small businesses, curb excessive overdraft fees, and prevent medical debt from showing up on credit reports is now coming to a halt. 

@HouseDemocrats won't stand for it. #HandsOffCFPB #ReopenCFPB
